                    Hi there! I'm Scott Dover, a software engineer at Research Square, a company on a mission to make
                    research publication faster and fairer for everyone.
                </h2>
                <p class="intro">
                    I'm also a budding cyclist, a proud member of the LGTBQIA+ community, an even prouder father, and am
