                    Before Research Square, I worked for Pursuit Of Happiness, the parent company of Everwondr: An
                    events management network that works closely with CVBs (Convention and Visitor Bureaus) around
                    North Carolina.
                </p>

                <p>
                    At Pursuit Of Happiness, I had the opportunity to re-build an events management system from the
                    ground up, as well as be the one-stop-shop for all things web-related. As the sole developer, every
                    layer of the webstack was my responsibility.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
